00:00:00,110 --> 00:00:01,179
Assalomu alaykum.

2
00:00:02,009 --> 00:00:04,209
Bugun juda qiziq
savolga javob beramiz.

3
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:06,639
Yaponiya ning oldini bormi?

4
00:00:07,460 --> 00:00:10,179
Dunyoda to'rt ming uch yuz
dan ortiq diniy e'tiqod

5
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:14,199
tizimlari mavjud Har bir
xalq oziga xos e'tiqodga ega.

6
00:00:15,030 --> 00:00:16,919
Yaponiyada esa bu
yanada qiziqroq.

7
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:18,529
Sintoizm.

8
00:00:19,310 --> 00:00:21,999
Sintoizm Yaponiya ning
o'ziga xos milliy diniy.

9
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:25,348
U tabiat guruhlarga va
ajdodlarga sig'inish

10
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:26,529
asosida shakllangan.

11
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:30,499
Shin to ibodatxonalari
toriy darvozalari, ruhlar

12
00:00:30,510 --> 00:00:33,299
bularning barchasi into
madaniyatining bir qismidir.

13
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:36,519
Hozirgi kunda yaponiyada
bir yuz yigirma uch

14
00:00:36,530 --> 00:00:37,909
milliondan ortiq aholi.

15
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:41,499
yashaydi Ularning yigirma
to'qqiz foizi oltmish.

16
00:00:41,510 --> 00:00:45,659
besh yoshdan katta o'n ikki
foizi esa o'n to'rt yoshgacha

17
00:00:45,670 --> 00:00:47,959
bo'lgan bolalar Yaponiyada.

18
00:00:48,820 --> 00:00:53,209
qirq sakkiz foiz odam sintoizm
ga e'tiqod qiladi o'ttiz besh

19
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:57,559
foiz buddizm tarafdori Qariyb
o'n olti foiz xristianlar

20
00:00:57,570 --> 00:00:58,519
yoki dinsizlar?

21
00:00:59,330 --> 00:00:59,989
Islomiylar.

